<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="still-adv">still <strong><em>adv</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /stɪl/    美 /stɪl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>还；仍然：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Even after two decades we still recognized each other.
虽然过去了二十年，我们仍然认得对方。</p><footer>2012 福建</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>然而；不过；虽然如此：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I would look up the words in the dictionary and still not fully understand the meanings.
我用词典查这些单词，然而还是不能完全理解它们的意思。</p><footer>2010 辽宁改</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>[修饰比较级] 更：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’s tall, but his brother is still taller.
他个子高，他哥哥更高。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Work hard to achieve still greater success.
努力工作以取得更大的成功。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>stillness /'stɪlnəs/ n [U]  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The hotel is almost finished, but it <strong><em>_</em></strong>__ needs one or two weeks to get ready for guests.  （2012 四川改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. still  </p></div>